Package: antanym
Title: An R package for the Antarctic geographic placenames, including the SCAR Composite Gazetteer of Antarctica
Version: 0.0.6
Authors@R: c(person("Ben", "Raymond", email = "ben.raymond@aad.gov.au", role = c("aut", "cre")),
	     person("Michael", "Sumner", email = "michael.sumner@aad.gov.au", role = "aut")
	     )
Description: Access to Antarctic geographic names, including the SCAR Composite Gazetteer of Antarctica,
    and functions for searching those place names.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0)
